# Harness immutability (feature work)

During normal feature implementation, **do not edit** harness configuration unless the user explicitly asks to update agent guidance.

- Edit application code under `{{SCOPE_GLOBS}}` only.
- Harness changes belong in a dedicated PR reviewed by {{HARNESS_OWNER}}.
- If a repeatable agent failure requires a harness fix, load skill `harness-self-improve` and apply a minimal canonical harness edit (allowed carve-out for self-improvement). Otherwise propose a minimal diff and stop.
